OL,3,CMan admits carrying knuckle-duster as
OL,4,Ccourts remain active over weekend
OL,6,FA scaffolder has admitted possessing a
OL,7,Fknuckle duster at a demonstration
OL,8,Fearlier this week as more people
OL,9,Fappeared in court over the weekend
OL,10,Ffollowing days of unrest in the UK.
OL,12,FLee James, 42, was arrested at his
OL,13,Fhome in Southampton after police were
OL,14,Ftold he had the weapon in Grosvenor
OL,15,FSquare, where a demonstration took
OL,16,Fplace on August 7.
OL,18,FBristol Magistrates' Court heard on
OL,19,FSaturday that James still had the
OL,20,Fknuckle duster in his pocket when he
OL,21,Fwas detained.
