OL,6,FDistrict Judge Lynne Matthews remanded
OL,7,FJames into custody ahead of his
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing at Southampton
OL,9,FCrown Court on August 12.
OL,11,FJames's appearance in front of the
OL,12,Fcourt on Saturday was one of many
OL,13,Ftaking place all over the country.
