OL,3,CMan admits carrying knuckle-duster as
OL,4,Ccourts remain active over weekend
OL,6,FLucy Connolly, 41, the partner of
OL,7,FConservative West Northamptonshire
OL,8,Fcouncillor Raymond Connolly, appeared
OL,9,Fat Nottingham Magistrates' Court on
OL,10,FSaturday charged with publishing
OL,11,Fwritten material to stir up racial
OL,12,Fhatred in relation to a social media
OL,13,Fmessage calling for attacks on asylum
OL,14,Fseekers.
OL,16,FShe did not enter a plea, via video
OL,17,Flink, and was remanded in custody
OL,18,Funtil her next appearance at
OL,19,FNorthampton Crown Court on Monday.
