OL,6,FIn South Yorkshire, three people have
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to violent disorder in
OL,8,FManvers, Rotherham on August 4, South
OL,9,FYorkshire Police said.
OL,11,FKaine Hicks, 22, of Wombwell Road,
OL,12,FPlatts Common; Drew Jarvis, 19, of no
OL,13,Ffixed address; and a 17-year-old boy,
OL,14,Fadmitted the offence at Sheffield
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday, the
OL,16,Fforce said.
